\ls1\ilvl0
\f2\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs26 steps(int, <jumpterm>): This creates a stepped transition, where the animation progresses in a series of discrete jumps rather than a smooth curve. The int value specifies the number of steps, and the optional <jumpterm> (e.g., start, end, jump-start, jump-end, jump-both, jump-none) controls how the steps are performed.\
