	Use 
\f0\b forwards
\f1\b0  if you want the element to 
\f3\i stay
\f1\i0  in its final position.\
	Use 
\f0\b backwards
\f1\b0  if you want the element to 
\f3\i start
\f1\i0  in its animated style even before the animation begins.\
	Use 
\f0\b both
\f1\b0  if you want 
\f3\i both behaviors
